    General Stores in Vile Parle East, Mumbai

    General Stores in Vile Parle East, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Vile Parle East, Mumbai from the list given above.
